org.sql: SELECT accounts.username, accounts.domain FROM accounts INNER JOIN blocks ON accounts.id = blocks.target_account_id WHERE blocks.account_id = "$1" ORDER BY blocks.id DESC

rewrites.sql: SELECT accounts.username, accounts.domain FROM accounts INNER JOIN blocks ON accounts.id = blocks.target_account_id WHERE blocks.account_id = "$1" ORDER BY blocks.id DESC LIMIT 1
